5.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>；該張實體專輯於5日發行。原定於11月2日公開音源之雙單曲《APOLOGY<ref>{{Citation|last=iKON|title=iKON - 지못미(APOLOGY) M/V|date=2015-11-15|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blSCDrx0CDA/|accessdate=2018-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919055948/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=blSCDrx0CDA|dead-url=no}}</ref>》、《ANTHEM<ref>{{Citation|last=iKON|title=iKON - 이리오너라(ANTHEM) M/V|date=2015-11-15|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdD7ciXKfzE/|accessdate=2018-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919055945/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdD7ciXKfzE|dead-url=no}}</ref>》於16日發布，發布後即在各大音樂排行榜佔據1位、2位<ref>[http://www.vlovekpop.com/ikon-%E5%85%A9%E9%A6%96%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%99%82%E6%A9%AB%E6%8E%83%E9%9F%B3%E6%BA%90%E6%A6%9C-mv%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88/ iKON兩首新歌同時橫掃音源榜，MV反應熱烈] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vlovekpop.com/ikon-%E5%85%A9%E9%A6%96%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C%E5%90%8C%E6%99%82%E6%A9%AB%E6%8E%83%E9%9F%B3%E6%BA%90%E6%A6%9C-mv%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E7%86%B1%E7%83%88/ |date=20160307175334 }}vlovekpop{{zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/70347|title=iKON16日發新單曲《[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qdD7ciXKfzE/ ANTHEM]》 B.I、BOBBY作詞作曲才華橫溢|date=2015-11-05|publisher=KSD韓星網|accessdate=2018-04-14|archive-date=2018-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302044628/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/70347|dead-url=no}}</ref>。（收錄12首曲目）正規專輯《WELCOME BACK》經歷所屬公司[[YG娛樂|YG娛樂]]多次宣布延期後，於12月24日正式發行，雙主打《DUMB & DUMBER<ref>{{Citation|last=iKON|title=iKON - 덤앤더머(DUMB&DUMBER) M/V|date=2015-12-23|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QjZkpm7_kRk/|accessdate=2018-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919055956/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QjZkpm7_kRk|dead-url=no}}</ref>》和《WHAT'S WRONG?<ref>{{Citation|last=iKON|title=iKON - 왜 또(WHAT'S WRONG?) M/V|date=2015-12-23|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KS2UujCafvQ/|accessdate=2018-03-23|archive-date=2019-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190919055943/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KS2UujCafvQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>》亦於各個韓國音樂榜單獲得1位至3位。
